name: Into the New World
description:
This work is a representation of me when I got to know NFT and joined the community.

No matter the day or night, artists and collectors from different regions/countries use their time to be more active in the community.

Interestingly, the Tezos Community looks very solid to me. Many artists support each other to grow together in the community.

There are many reasons why artists join NFT. Whatever our reasons, may luck always be with us, and we will be successful in what we do. 

A reminder for me and for my fellow artists who have just joined and started their NFT path; when you feel burnout, art block, or in bad condition, it's okay to take a short break before continuing to work again. However, health conditions also need to be considered.

Also, thank you so much to the collectors and fellow artists who have helped new artists by collecting their work. Your support means a lot.
